OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMexico tightens ban on     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsmoking in public places   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Mexico has brought into force one of   
OL,6, the world's strictest anti-tobacco laws
OL,7, by enacting a total ban on smoking in  
OL,8, public places.                         
OL,10,FThe step, which was first approved in  
OL,11,F2021, also includes a ban on tobacco   
OL,12,Fadvertising.                           
OL,14,FSeveral other Latin American countries 
OL,15,Fhave also passed legislation to create 
OL,16,Fsmoke-free public spaces.              
OL,18,FHowever, Mexico's legislation is       
OL,19,Fconsidered to be the most robust and   
OL,20,Fwide-ranging in the Americas.          
